  triage:title "Python unittest fixture tests for valid/invalid-schema/duplicate inventory cases absent from .just/tests/" ;
  triage:description ".just/tests/ contains no Python unittest fixture tests for the boundary inventory loader. Sprint A.6 requires fixture tests covering at minimum: (1) valid schema load, (2) invalid schema rejection, (3) duplicate inventory detection. These tests parity-check the Rust sc-lint-boundary loader via the Python oracle. Fix: add .just/tests/test_lint_boundaries.py (or equivalent) with unittest cases for valid, invalid-schema, and duplicate-inventory scenarios." ;
